title: LEGO Star Wars 75393 TIE Fighter & X-Wing Mash-up - Building Toy with 2 Starships, 4 Minifigures and a Droid Figure, Creative Gift for 9+ Year Old Boys and Fans
features: LEGO Star Wars vehicle Mash-up – Create mixed-up ‘TIE-wing’ and ‘X-fighter’ starfighters, as seen in the Rebuild the Galaxy Disney+ special with this buildable Star Wars toy for 9+ year old boys and girls
4 LEGO Star Wars minifigures – Rebel Pilot and TIE Pilot with blaster pistols, Yesi Scala, Sig Greebling, plus an L3-G0 Star Wars LEGO droid figure
Star Wars building set – Each starfighter has an opening cockpit for a minifigure, spring-loaded shooters, and the X-wing’s wings are adjustable
Creative building toys for kids – Remove the locking pins to detach the wings of the models and rebuild them into a classic TIE fighter and an X-wing
Star Wars gift for kids – This brick-built adventure toy playset makes a fun birthday gift for 9+ year old boys, girls and older Star Wars fans
Part of the LEGO Star Wars: Rebuild the Galaxy collection – Look out for 75388 Jedi Bob’s Starfighter and 75389 The Dark Falcon sets, sold separately
Fun LEGO Star Wars sets for all ages – LEGO Star Wars building toys allow kids and adult fans to recreate iconic scenes, dream up original stories or display the buildable models
description: From the manufacturer Build your own mixed-up starfighters! Recreate mash-up starfighters from the LEGO Star Wars: Rebuild the Galaxy Disney+ special with this buildable kids’ set. Rebuildable starfighter building toys Spark children’s creativity with this fun LEGO Star Wars set featuring ‘TIE-wing’ and ‘X-fighter’ brick-built models. LEGO Star Wars TIE Fighter & X-Wing Mash-Up TIE-wing Combine the hull of an X-wing with a TIE fighter’s wings. X-fighter Connect the hull of a TIE fighter with an X-wing’s wings. Opening cockpits Place a LEGO minifigure in the cockpit of each starfighter. Built for action Each mash-up starfighter has 2 spring-loaded shooters. Easy to rebuild Rebuild to create the iconic TIE Fighter and X-wing. 5 LEGO Star Wars characters Includes Sig Greebling and a L3-G0 droid LEGO figure. Inspiring gifts for kids Explore the LEGO Star Wars range and discover other cool building sets (sold separately) for even more play options.
